casebody.data:
Constance Sacramone, an Infant, by Her Father and Natural Guardian, Dario Sacramone, et al., Appellants, v David Tunick, Respondent. Submitted January 10, 1977; decided February 10, 1977

Reported below, 54 AD2d 897.

Motion to dismiss the appeal herein granted and the appeal dismissed, without costs, upon the ground that the order appealed from involves an exercise of discretion of the type not reviewable by the Court of Appeals.
